{
  "stem": "18654.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they persuaded me on the strength of them coming to collect me-- or us, I should say-- within three months.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, I don't know if all children-- because I can came on a children's transport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we only had permission to stay, I believe, for six months in England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But of course, this was altered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I-- I believed them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So on these grounds, I came to England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we left on January-- I don't, it must have been the 17th, I think, because we arrived in England on the 18th.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it was an overnight journey.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember being taken with my sister to the Frankfurt station, and we were put on a train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the last time I saw my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We traveled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember traveling through Holland, where food was passed to us through the window of the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was the first time I saw tea with milk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And none of us knew what it was because we'd never seen this before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that-- that stuck in my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the next thing I remember on the boat, which must have been an overnight journey.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was an overnight journey because we were in bunks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember putting a little chain next to me in the container, in case you were ill in the night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had this chain between two containers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I forgot it when they were told to get up and leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remembered it afterwards and I rushed back and I still found the chain, which I brought to England.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the next thing I remember is London, coming out on a train to London.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
